```

thinking about his. maybe it is indeed a better idea to not scan the .part file and also skip triggering of hooks for it completely. otherwise all hooks will be triggered once for the .part file and once for the renamed file. this will cause sgnificant overhed for the sync client.

pulling @danimo @dragotin and @icewind1991 here to let them know i'll try to create a solution that does not trigger any hooks

